UID:F5oSduPvWwulPc43bOUCB
SUMMARY:Punk Rock Garage Sale
DTSTAMP:20260617T163157Z
DTSTART:20260621T140000Z
DESCRIPTION:Insomnia Gallery and Deep End Records are excited to announce t
	he date for our July Punk Rock Garage Sale!\n\nIf you haven’t caught on ye
	t\, these happen on the 3rd Sunday of EVERY MONTH at Bad Astronaut brewing
	!\n\nWhile summer is heating up\, stay relatively cool as this event is **
	*ALL INDOORS!*** and the event space itself now has AC!\n\nThere will be O
	VER 50 VENDORS inside this massive adult playground of a venue which featu
	res pool tables\, foosball\, air hockey\, cornhole and more (and all FREE 
	to play!)\n\nWe’ve got makers\, artists\, collectibles\, thrift and vintag
	e\, music\, books\, video games\, movies and vendors selling so much more!
	\nIf you’re looking for a gift or to treat yourself\, come to Insomnia Gal
	lery’s Punk Rock Garage Sale for a true chance to score!\n\nNEW VENDORS EV
	ERY MONTH! We’ll mix in a few pro vendors and artists as well to bring you
	 a truly unique market each and every month!\n\nAbout this event:Based on 
	the punk rock garage sales that took place regularly at Walter’s Downtown\
	, Insomnia Gallery has been keeping this tradition alive for the last 6 ye
	ars! DIY Forever!\nSale hours: 2:00pm – 6:00pm\nLocation: Bad Astronaut Br
	ewing at 1519 Fulton\nFREE street parking on Sunday in addition to their b
	ack parking lot and grass parking lot!\n\n** INTERESTED IN SETTING UP? Con
	tact deependhtx@gmail.com with a general description of the items you’d li
	ke to sell and we’ll get back with you asap! Table fee ranges from $15-$25
	 depending on setup size!\n\nhttps://badastronautbeer.com/event/punk-rock-
	garage-sale-3/2026-06-21/\n\nFrom Bad Astronaut Brewery
URL:https://badastronautbeer.com/event/punk-rock-garage-sale-3/2026-06-21/
LOCATION:Bad Astronaut Brewery\, 1519 Fulton Street\, Houston\, TX\, 77009\
	, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:bad-astronaut-brewery
CATEGORIES:Bad Astronaut Brewery
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT4H
END:VEVENT
